videos.description: The ball gets kicked out to Gabe DeVoe who sinks in a 3-pointer from the wing.
videos.headline: Clemson's DeVoe drains triple

videos.description: Marcquise Reed drains easy triple from the top of the arc.
videos.headline: Tigers' Reed sinks 3-pointer

videos.description: Terance Mann goes in for the drive and gets fouled on the play, he later makes the free throw.
videos.headline: Florida State's Mann zips his way to the hoop

videos.description: Florida State capitalizes off of two Tigers' turnovers with back-to-back dunks.
videos.headline: Back-to-back dunks for the Seminoles

videos.description: Terance Mann attempts a jumper and misses, then Phil Cofer slams it home for a putback jam.
videos.headline: Florida State's Cofer with a putback jam

videos.description: Braian Angola intercepts a pass and finds Terance Mann fir the lay-in.
videos.headline: Seminoles' Angola with a steal-and-score

videos.description: Trent Forrest drives into the paint with seconds left on the clock, and makes the lay-in forcing overtime.
videos.headline: Florida State's Forrest forces OT with a driving layup

videos.description: Florida State takes the lead for the first time in this game off of a fancy spin lay-in from Trent Forrest.
videos.headline: Florida State takes the lead for first time

videos.description: Shelton Mitchell gets hit in the head with an elbow, and is attended to by medical staff and is later carried off the court.
videos.headline: Clemson's Mitchell is carried off the court with apparent head injury
